WEBVTT

00:03.560 --> 00:06.160
Including your sister. So if you
love her and want to take her alive

00:06.280 --> 00:07.200
tell me where she is.

00:07.320 --> 00:08.920
I love you. I'm sorry!

00:09.040 --> 00:10.120
Daddy!

00:10.320 --> 00:11.636
Seven years!

00:12.237 --> 00:14.415
All it would have taken was one message

00:14.416 --> 00:16.392
just to put me out of my misery.

00:16.399 --> 00:18.400
No. I couldn't risk Ariel finding us.

00:18.480 --> 00:21.200
Celine, I've been a priest for 20 years.

00:21.360 --> 00:24.800
I've never broken my vows, and
I don't think you should, either.

00:26.040 --> 00:29.400
- I love you.
- This is bigger than us.

00:29.560 --> 00:30.680
Frankie!

00:30.800 --> 00:32.680
She's gone!

00:32.800 --> 00:35.000
Your brother.

00:37.000 --> 00:43.074
